<title>UK: Bruntcliffe shares up on possible takeover.</title>
<headline>Bruntcliffe shares up on possible takeover.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares in British quarrying group Bruntcliffe Aggregates Plc rose on Friday after the company said it was in discussions that may lead to it receiving a takeover offer.</p>
<p>The stock was 3-1/2p higher to 36p at 0815 GMT.</p>
<p>The company said it did not expect an offer to be made imminently.</p>
